bc89cd4.png</a>"},{"pid":"c7a0e0ed1aa0cda3e19b87a567caeae4509ff6cc","tid":761250,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T09:59:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/011226_eba6400fe2bfe149f90560d62bc89cd4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F011226_eba6400fe2bfe149f90560d62bc89cd4.png&h=d3057e31&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"575a0d5fe1855a542be6fa5a3577204305dd9b2b","tid":761250,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T09:59:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/011226_eba6400fe2bfe149f90560d62bc89cd4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F011226_eba6400fe2bfe149f90560d62bc89cd4.png&h=d3057e31&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41704e0a6244353a32dfd4a4e5b877e114d6d25f","tid":761250,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T10:06:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">創科獲撥款500億 楊偉雄：長遠1,000億都唔夠</span><br />\n<br />\n預算案宣佈預留近500億元作為發展創新科技的基建投資和吸納人才，當中200億元將投放在落馬洲河套區港深創新及科技園。創新及科技局局長楊偉雄今早在電台節目中表示，期望香港「科技研發」的本地生產總值（GDP）能達450億元，比現時僅180億元增加1.5倍。他重申預算案在創科投放500億元是「穩健、非常合適」的做法，但長遠即使投放1,000億元都不足夠。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180302/57893431\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180302%2F57893431&d=tvKTabl%2B8AIuEaxwPSc4YW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=d4d86ea5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180302%2F57893431&h=a2fe72c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180302/57893431</a>"},{"pid":"56e44cdd53f2eb21459d0bb463d0bea05c0543f0","tid":761250,"uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quo